      <title>中国的通货紧缩螺旋正进入危险的新阶段</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/china-s-deflationary-spiral-is-now-entering-dangerous-new-stage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自去年以来困扰中国的通货紧缩目前有进一步加剧的迹象，这可能会恶化这个世界第二大经济体的前景，并引发要求中国立即采取政策行动的呼声。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/china-s-deflationary-spiral-is-now-entering-dangerous-new-stage</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 10:30:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报道称，巴厘岛寻求两年内禁止建造新酒店和俱乐部</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/bali-seeks-two-year-ban-on-building-new-hotels-and-clubs-antara</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据印尼国家通讯社安塔拉报道，巴厘岛省政府提议暂时禁止建造新的酒店、别墅、迪斯科舞厅和海滩俱乐部，以减缓土地开发速度和岛屿过度拥挤现象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/bali-seeks-two-year-ban-on-building-new-hotels-and-clubs-antara</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 10:16:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
